high_descs: Head to the bathroom on the left of the hallway to reach the bathtub.
Pick up the knife from the bathtub.
Turn around and head to the bedroom on the right to reach the nightstand.
Cut the apple on the nightstand into pieces with the knife.
Move left to exit the bedroom and take a right to reach the white table to the left of the kitchen.
Put the knife on the right edge of the table.
Turn around and walk back to the bedroom nightstand to the right of the hallway.
Pick up a slice of apple from the nightstand.
Head right into the bathroom on the right to face the sink.
Wash the slice of apple in the sink and pick it up.
Take a left to reach the end of the hallway and take a right to reach the white table.
Put the apple slice on the table in front of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife and washed slice of an apple on the table.

high_descs: Walk left to head down the hallway and head to the second room on the left to reach the bathtub in the bathroom.
Pick up the knife from the bathtub.
Turn around and head to the room on the right, walk down the passage to reach the bedroom and head to the nightstand on the left.
Cut the apple into slices with the knife.
Turn around to exit the bedroom; turn left to head down the hallway and turn right to reach the kitchen and head to the white table on the right.
Put the knife on the right of the table.
Turn around to exit the kitchen; turn left to head down the hallway; turn right to enter the bedroom to reach the nightstand on the left of the bed.
Pick up a slice of apple from the nightstand.
Turn around, head right to walk up to the table, turn left to exit the room, turn left and enter the bathroom on the right to reach the sink.
Wash the slice of apple in the sink and take it out.
Exit the bathroom, turn right to head down the hallway, turn right to head to the white table in the kitchen.
Put the slice of apple on the table in front of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed slice of apple on the table.

high_descs: walk to the end of the hallway and go to the bathtub.
pick up the butterknife from the sink.
take a left then turn right and go straight to get into the apple.
go to the apple in the nightstand in the bedroom.
cut the apple that is on the diningtable.
turn around and go through the hallway to get to the diningtable.
walk back to the sidetable.
pick up a piece of the cut apple.
take the apple and go to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
wash it and then remove it from the diningtable.
go to the diningtable and put the apple down on top of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: go to the room and get a piece of apple from the diningtable.

high_descs: Head down the passage in the front and turn left to reach the bathroom to face the bathtub.
Pick up the butterknife from the tub.
Turn around to exit the bathroom and turn left to walk across the room and turn right to reach the apple on the bedroom nightstand on the left.
Cut the apple on the nightstand with the knife.
Turn around to walk out of the bedroom on the left and turn left to walk into the kitchen on the right and reach the dining table.
Put the butterknife on the diningtable.
Turn around to exit the kitchen and head to the bedroom on the right and reach the sidetable on the left of the bed.
Pick up the apple from the nightstand.
Turn around and head down the passage on the left and take a left turn to walk across the room and take a left turn to head down the passage and turn right to reach the sink.
Wash the apple slice in the sink and take the apple slice out.
Turn right to exit the bathroom and head down the passage on the right and turn right to reach the dining table.
Put the apple slice on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Apple slice on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the bathtub.
Take the butterknife from the sink.
Turn around and go to the bedroom.
Cut the apple into pieces using the knife on the side table.
Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Put the butterknife on the diningtable.
Turn around and go to the sidetable.
Take the apple from the side table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the apple into the sink and wash it.
Then take it out and go near the diningtable.
Put the apple on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the knife and piece of apple on the diningtable.

high_descs: Head to the hallway ahead and to the left, then go through the hallway until reaching the bathtub on the left, entering it.
Pick up the butterknife from the bathtub.
Exit the bathroom and head into the room on the opposite wall to the left, then go to the wall, turn right and go through this area to the apple next to the bed.
Slice the apple on the bedstand.
Walk around the bed to exit this room back to the hallway, turn left and go all the way forward, then right towards the white dining table.
Place the butterknife down on the diningtable.
Return to the sidetable with the sliced apple.
Pick up one slice of the apple slice.
Exit the room through the narrow path near the bedstand again, then turn left and go ahead back into the hallway, entering the bathroom you got the knife from the sink.
Wash the apple slice in the sink and pick the apple slice back up.
Exit the bathroom, turn right and go ahead to the dining table you placed the knife on.
Place the apple slice down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed Apple slice on a DiningTable.
